name: MySQL5
queryCode:
SELECT
	t1.`BRANCH`,
	t1.`DELETED`,
	t1.`GRADE`,
	t1.`ID`,
	'module' AS `DOCQTYPE`,
	1 AS `ISFAVOURITES`,
	( CASE WHEN EXISTS ( SELECT 1 FROM ZT_MODULE WHERE PARENT = t1.`ID` ) THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END ) AS `ISLEAF`,
	t1.`NAME`,
	t1.`ORDER`,
	t1.`OWNER`,
	t1.`PARENT`,
	t1.`PATH`,
	t1.`ROOT`,
	t1.`SHORT`,
	t1.`TYPE` 
FROM
	`zt_module` t1
